\c 28
\s Izibusiso zokulalela
\p
\v 1 Kuzakuthi-ke, uba ulalela lokulalela ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukugcina ukwenza yonke imilayo yayo engikulaya yona lamuhla\x + Eks. 15.26. Levi 26.3. Isa. 55.2.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakumisa phezulu phezu kwazo zonke izizwe zomhlaba\x + 26.19.\x*.
\v 2 Lalezizibusiso zonke zizakuza phezu kwakho, zikufice, nxa ulalela ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 28.15. Zek. 1.6.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Uzabusiswa emzini, ubusiswe futhi ensimini\x + Gen. 39.5.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Sizabusiswa isithelo sesizalo sakho, lesithelo somhlaba wakho, lenzalo yezifuyo zakho\x + 28.11,18,53. Dute. 7.13. Gen. 49.25. Dute. 30.9. 1 Tim. 4.8.\x*, umqegu wenkomo zakho, lamazinyane ezimvu zakho\x + 28.11,18,53. Dute. 7.13. Gen. 49.25. Dute. 30.9. 1 Tim. 4.8.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Kuzabusiswa isitsha sakho\x + 26.2.\x*, lomganu wakho wokuxovela izinkwa.
\p
\v 6 Uzabusiswa ekungeneni kwakho, ubusiswe ekuphumeni kwakho\x + Hlab. 121.8.\x*.
\p
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza izitha zakho ezikuvukelayo zitshaywe phambi kwakho; zizaphuma ukumelana lawe ngandlelanye, zibaleke phambi kwakho ngezindlela eziyisikhombisa\x + Levi 26.7,8. 2 Sam. 22.38-41. Hlab. 18.37-40. 18.25.\x*.
\p
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* izalaya isibusiso phezu kwakho, eziphaleni zakho\x + Levi 25.21.\x* lakukho konke obeka kukho isandla sakho, ikubusise elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona\x + 12.7.\x*.
\p
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* izazimisela wena ube yisizwe esingcwele, njengokufunga kwayo kuwe, uba ugcina imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, uhambe endleleni zayo\x + Eks. 19.5,6. Dute. 7.6; 26.18,19. 29.13.\x*.
\v 10 Labo bonke abantu basemhlabeni bazabona ukuthi ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* libizwa phezu kwakho\x + Nani 6.27.\x*, bakwesabe\x + 11.25.\x*.
\v 11 LeN\nd kosi\nd* izakwandisela okuhle, esithelweni sesizalo sakho, lenzalweni yezifuyo zakho, lesithelweni somhlaba wakho, elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyafungela oyihlo ukukunika lona\x + 30.9.\x*.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakuvulela okuligugu kwayo okulungileyo, amazulu, ukunika izulu elizweni lakho ngesikhathi salo\x + 11.14. Levi 26.4.\x*, lokubusisa umsebenzi wonke wesandla sakho\x + 14.29.\x*; njalo uzakweboleka izizwe ezinengi, kodwa wena ungeboleki \add kuzo\x + 15.6. 28.44.\x*\add*.
\v 13 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza ube yinhloko, ungabi ngumsila; uzakuba ngaphezulu kuphela, ungabi ngaphansi, uba ulalela imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho engikulaya yona lamuhla ukuyigcina lokuyenza\x + Isa. 9.14,15. Dute. 15.6.\x*.
\v 14 Ungaphambuki lakwelilodwa lamazwi engililaya wona lamuhla, ukuya ngakwesokunene langakwesokhohlo, ukulandela abanye onkulunkulu ukubakhonza\x + 5.32.\x*.
\s Iziqalekiso zokungalaleli
\p
\v 15 Kodwa kuzakuthi, uba ungalaleli ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukugcina ukwenza yonke imilayo yayo lezimiso zayo engikulaya zona lamuhla, leziziqalekiso zonke zize phezu kwakho\x + Levi 26.14. Lilo 2.17. Dan. 9.11,13. Mal. 2.2.\x* zikufice\x + 28.2.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Uzaqalekiswa emzini, uqalekiswe futhi ensimini\x + 28.3-6.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Kuzaqalekiswa isitsha sakho lomganu wakho wokuxovela izinkwa.
\p
\v 18 Kuzaqalekiswa isithelo sesizalo sakho, lesithelo somhlaba wakho, umqegu wenkomo zakho, lamazinyane ezimvu zakho.
\p
\v 19 Uzaqalekiswa ekungeneni kwakho, uqalekiswe ekuphumeni kwakho.
\p
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* izathumela phakathi kwakho isiqalekiso\x + Mal. 2.2.\x*, inhlupheko\x + 7.23. 1 Sam. 14.20. Zek. 14.13.\x*, lokukhuza\x + Hlab. 80.16. Isa. 30.17. 51.20. 66.15.\x*, kukho konke obeka isandla sakho kukho ukukwenza, uze uchithwe, njalo uze ubhubhe masinyane, ngenxa yobubi bezenzo zakho, ongidele ngazo\x + 12.7.\x*.
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* izanamathelisa kuwe umatshayabhuqe wesifo, aze akuqede usuke elizweni oya kulo ukudla ilifa lalo\x + Levi 26.25.\x*.
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakutshaya ngesifo esicakisayo\x + Levi 26.16.\x*, langoqhuqho, langokuvuvuka komzimba, langokutshisa okukhulukazi, langenkemba\x + Levi 26.16.\x*, langokuhanguka\x + 1 Kho. 8.37. Amos 4.9. Hag. 2.17.\x*, langengumane\x + 1 Kho. 8.37. Amos 4.9. Hag. 2.17.\x*; njalo kuzakuxotsha uze ubhubhe.
\v 23 Lesibhakabhaka sakho esiphezu kwekhanda lakho sizakuba lithusi, lomhlaba ongaphansi kwakho ube yinsimbi\x + Levi 26.19.\x*.
\v 24 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza izulu lelizwe lakho libe lubhuqu lothuli, kwehlele phezu kwakho kuvela emazulwini, uze ubhujiswe.
\v 25 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza utshaywe phambi kwezitha zakho; uzaphuma umelane lazo ngandlelanye, njalo uzabaleka phambi kwazo ngezindlela eziyisikhombisa\x + 28.7. Levi 26.17,37 Dute. 32.30. Isa. 30.17.\x*; uzakuba yinto eyesabekayo kuyo yonke imibuso yomhlaba\x + Jer. 15.4. 24.9. 29.18. 34.17. Hez. 23.46. 2 Lan. 29.8. Isa. 28.19.\x*.
\v 26 Lesidumbu sakho sizakuba yikudla kwenyoni zonke zamazulu lokwezinyamazana zomhlaba\x + Hlab. 79.2. Jer. 7.33. 16.4. 34.20. 1 Sam. 17.44,46.\x*, njalo kungabi khona ozethusayo\x + Jer. 7.33. Levi 26.6.\x*.
\v 27 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakutshaya ngamathumba eGibhithe\x + 28.35. Levi 13.18.\x*, lamaqhubu\x + 1 Sam. 5.6.\x*, loqweqwe, lenkomo, ongelakwelatshwa kukho\x + Levi 21.20. 22.22.\x*.
\v 28 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakutshaya ngobuhlanya langobuphofu\x + 2 Kho. 9.20. Zek. 12.4. Dute. 28.34.\x* langokudideka kwenhliziyo\x + Zek. 12.4. Jer. 4.9.\x*.
\v 29 Njalo uzaphumputha emini njengesiphofu siphumputha emnyameni, ungenzi indlela zakho ziphumelele; ucindezelwe kuphela, uphangwe insuku zonke, kungabi khona osindisayo\x + Jobe 5.14. Isa. 59.10.\x*.
\v 30 Uzagana umfazi, kodwa enye indoda ilale laye\x + 20.5-7.\x*; uzakwakha indlu, kodwa ungahlali kuyo; uhlanyele isivini, kodwa ungakhi izithelo zaso\x + Amos 5.11. Zef. 1.13.\x*.
\v 31 Inkabi yakho izahlatshwa phambi kwamehlo akho, ungadli okwayo; ubabhemi wakho athathwe ngodlakela phambi kobuso bakho, angabuyiselwa kuwe; izimvu zakho zizanikwa izitha zakho, kungabi khona okusindiselayo.
\v 32 Amadodana akho lamadodakazi akho azanikelwa kwesinye isizwe, lamehlo akho azakhangela abalangathe usuku lonke\x + Hlab. 69.3. 119.82,123.\x*; kodwa kungabi lamandla esandleni sakho\x + Gen. 31.29. Zaga 3.27.\x*.
\v 33 Isithelo somhlaba wakho, lomsebenzi wakho wonke, isizwe ongasaziyo sizakudla. Uzacindezelwa kuphela, uchotshozwe insuku zonke\x + 28.29.\x*,
\v 34 uze uhlanye ngenxa yokubona kwamehlo akho ozakubona\x + 28.67.\x*.
\v 35 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakutshaya emadolweni lemilenzeni ngamathumba amabi angelakwelatshwa, kusukela kungaphansi yonyawo lwakho kuze kube senkanda yakho\x + 28.27.\x*.
\v 36 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakusa wena lenkosi yakho owayibeka phezu kwakho esizweni ongasaziyo wena laboyihlo\x + 2 Kho. 17.4,6. 24.12,14. 25.7,11. 2 Lan. 33.11. 36.6,20.\x*, ukhonze lapho abanye onkulunkulu, isigodo lelitshe\x + 4.28. 28.64.\x*.
\v 37 Uzakuba yinto eyesabekayo\x + 1 Kho. 9.7,8. Jer. 24.9. 25.9.\x*, isaga\x + Hlab. 44.14. Hez. 14.8.\x*, lenhlekisa phakathi kwazo zonke izizwe\x + 1 Kho. 9.7,8. Jer. 24.9. 25.9.\x*, lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* ezakusa khona.
\v 38 Uzaphuma lenhlanyelo enengi uye ensimini, kodwa ubuthelele okulutshwana\x + Hag. 1.6. Mika 6.15.\x*, ngoba isikhonyane sizakudla\x + Jow. 1.4. 2.25.\x*.
\v 39 Uzahlanyela izivini, uzisebenze, kodwa kawuyikunatha iwayini, kawuyikubutha \add lutho\add*, ngoba imihogoyi izazidla.
\v 40 Uzakuba lezihlahla zemihlwathi phakathi kwemingcele yakho yonke, kodwa kawuyikugcoba ngamafutha, ngoba imihlwathi izawohloka.
\v 41 Uzazala amadodana lamadodakazi, kodwa kawayikuba ngawakho, ngoba azakuya ekuthunjweni\x + Lilo 1.5.\x*.
\v 42 Zonke izihlahla zakho lezithelo zomhlaba wakho zizakuba ngezesikhonyane.
\v 43 Owemzini ophakathi kwakho uzaphakama phezu kwakho aqonge phezulu, wena-ke uzakwehlela phansi phansi\x + 28.13.\x*.
\v 44 Yena uzakweboleka, kodwa wena ungameboleki\x + 28.12.\x*; yena uzakuba yinhloko, kodwa wena ube ngumsila\x + 28.13.\x*.
\v 45 Lazo zonke leziziqalekiso zizakwehlela, zixotshane lawe, zikufice, uze ubhujiswe, ngoba ungalilalelanga ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukugcina imilayo yayo lezimiso zayo eyakulaya zona\x + 28.15.\x*.
\v 46 Njalo zizakuba phezu kwakho ukuba yisibonakaliso lokuba yisimangaliso, laphezu kwenzalo yakho kuze kube nininini.
\v 47 Njengoba ungayikhonzanga\x + Isa. 8.18.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ngentokozo langokuhle kwenhliziyo\x + Isa. 65.14.\x*, ngenxa yobunengi bakho konke\x + 32.15.\x*,
\v 48 ngakho uzakhonza izitha zakho iN\nd kosi\nd* ezazithuma ukumelana lawe, endlaleni, lekomeni, lekuhambenize, lekusweleni konke. Njalo izabeka ijogwe lensimbi entanyeni yakho, ize ikubhubhise.\x + Jer. 28.14.\x*
\v 49 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakuvusela isizwe esivela khatshana, emkhawulweni womhlaba\x + Jer. 5.15. 6.22,23. Luka 19.43.\x*, njengokuphapha kokhozi, isizwe olimi lwaso ongayikuluzwa\x + Jer. 48.40. 49.22. Lilo 4.19. Hez. 17.3. Hos. 8.1. Hab. 1.8.\x*,
\v 50 isizwe esilobuso obesabekayo, esingemukeli ubuso bomdala, esingelamusa komutsha\x + 2 Lan. 36.17. Isa. 47.6.\x*.
\v 51 Sizakudla isithelo sezifuyo zakho lesithelo somhlaba wakho, uze ubhujiswe; okungayikukutshiyela amabele, iwayini elitsha, lamafutha, umqegu wenkomo zakho, lamazinyane ezimvu zakho, size sikuchithe\x + 28.33. Isa. 62.8. Dute. 28.4.\x*.
\v 52 Sizakuvimbezela emasangweni akho wonke, ize idilike imiduli yakho ephakemeyo lebiyelwe ngemithangala obuthembela kuyo, elizweni lonke lakho; njalo sizakuvimbezela emasangweni akho wonke elizweni lonke lakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunike lona\x + 2 Kho. 25.1,2,4.\x*.
\v 53 Njalo uzakudla isithelo sesizalo sakho, inyama yamadodana leyamadodakazi akho, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunike wona\x + Levi 26.29. Dute. 28.57. Jer. 19.9. 2 Kho. 6.28,29. Lilo 2.20. 4.10.\x*, ekuvinjezelweni lekucindezelweni, izitha zakho ezizakucindezela ngakho\x + 28.55,57.\x*.
\v 54 Indoda ebuthakathaka phakathi kwakho letotoziweyo kakhulu, ilihlo layo lizakuba libi kumfowabo\x + 15.9.\x*, lakumka\add yo\add* wesifuba sayo, lakunsali yabantwana bayo ezabatshiya\x + 13.6.\x*;
\v 55 ukuze inganiki lamunye wabo okwenyama yabantwana bayo ebadlayo, ngoba ingasalelwanga lutho ekuvinjezelweni lekucindezelweni, izitha zakho ezizakucindezela ngakho emasangweni akho wonke\x + 28.55,57.\x*.
\v 56 Owesifazana obuthakathaka lototoziweyo phakathi kwakho ongazamanga ukubeka ingaphansi yonyawo lwakhe emhlabathini ngenxa yokutotozwa lobuthakathaka\x + 28.54. Isa. 47.1.\x*, ilihlo lakhe lizakuba libi endodeni yesifuba sakhe, lasendodaneni yakhe, lasendodakazini yakhe\x + 15.9.\x*,
\v 57 lakumnakwabo ophuma phakathi kwenyawo zakhe, lebantwaneni azabazala\x + Gen. 49.10.\x*; ngoba uzabadla ensitha ngenxa yokuswela konke, ekuvinjezelweni lekucindezelweni, isitha sakho esizakucindezela ngakho emasangweni akho\x + 28.55,57.\x*.
\p
\v 58 Uba ungayikugcina ukwenza wonke amazwi alumlayo abhaliweyo egwalweni lolu, ukwesaba lelibizo elilodumo lelesabekayo, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho,
\v 59 iN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza-ke inhlupheko zakho zimangalise, lenhlupheko zenzalo yakho, inhlupheko ezinkulu leziqhubekayo, lemikhuhlane emibi leqhubekayo\x + Hlab. 17.7. 31.21.\x*.
\v 60 Njalo izabuyisela kuwe zonke izifo zeGibhithe owawuzesaba, zizanamathela kuwe\x + 7.15.\x*,
\v 61 lawo wonke umkhuhlane layo yonke inhlupheko engabhalwanga egwalweni lwalumlayo, iN\nd kosi\nd* izakwehlisela zona uze ubhujiswe.
\v 62 Njalo lizasala lilabantu abalutshwana\x + 26.5.\x*, endaweni yokuthi lalinjengenkanyezi zamazulu ngobunengi, ngoba kawulalelanga ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 10.22. Neh. 9.23. Gen. 15.5.\x*.
\v 63 Kuzakuthi-ke, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* yathokoza ngani ukulenzela okuhle lokulandisa\x + 30.9. Jer. 32.41. Zef. 3.17. Isa. 62.5. 65.19.\x*, ngokunjalo iN\nd kosi\nd* izajabula ngani ukulichitha lokuliqeda, lihluthunwe elizweni ongena kulo ukudla ilifa lalo\x + Zaga 1.26. Isa. 1.24. Hez. 5.13.\x*.
\v 64 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakuhlakazela-ke phakathi kwezizwe zonke, kusukela komunye umkhawulo womhlaba kuze kube komunye umkhawulo womhlaba\x + Levi 26.33. Jer. 16.13.\x*, ukhonze lapho abanye onkulunkulu, wena laboyihlo elingabazanga, isigodo lelitshe\x + 28.36.\x*.
\v 65 Laphakathi kwalezozizwe kawuyikuphumula, lengaphansi yonyawo lwakho kayiyikuba lendawo yokuphumula\x + Amos 9.4.\x*; kodwa lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* izakupha inhliziyo ethuthumelayo\x + Levi 26.36.\x*, lokufiphala kwamehlo\x + Levi 26.16.\x*, lokudangala komphefumulo\x + Levi 26.16.\x*.
\v 66 Lempilo yakho izahlala isevalweni phambi kwakho; uzatshaywa luvalo ebusuku lemini, ungabi lethemba lempilo yakho.
\v 67 Ekuseni uzakuthi: Kungathi kungahlwa! Lakusihlwa uzakuthi: Kungathi kungasa! ngenxa yokwesaba kwenhliziyo ozakwesaba ngakho\x + Jobe 7.4.\x*, langenxa yokubona kwamehlo akho ozakubona\x + 28.34.\x*.
\v 68 LeN\nd kosi\nd* izakubuyisela eGibhithe ngemikhumbi, ngendlela engatsho ngayo kuwe \add ukuthi\x + Hos. 8.13. 9.3. Jer. 43.7.\x*\add*: Kawusayikuyibona futhi. Lapho lizazithengisa ezitheni zakho libe yizigqili lezigqilikazi, kodwa kakuyikuba lomthengi\x + 17.16.\x*.